## FORMAT (the emitted block)
```markdown
## [Low / Medium / High] Priority
***
#### What was Observed
[Security Tool] alerted on `[Rule / Detection Name]` with the following details:
* Host: `[Hostname]` | User: `[Domain\Username]` | Time (UTC): `[Timestamp]`
* Process: `[name]`
* File Name: `[name]`
* File Path: `[path]`
* Hash ([Type]): `[hash]`
  - [VirusTotal](https://www.virustotal.com/gui/search/[hash]) — [N/M malicious, only if enrichment produced it]
* Command Line: `[command]`
  * Decoded: `[Base64/encoded originals]`
* Parent Process: `[name]` | `[cmdline]`
* Child Process: `[name]` | `[cmdline]`
* Network / IOC: [defanged public IP/domain/URL OR plain private]
  - [VirusTotal — typed per IOC rules; enrichment stats if produced]
* Context: [Only if it passes Context Discipline. ≤2 total. Often zero. For action-taken, one bullet notes proactive reversible suppression.]
***
#### What is the Risk
* MITRE ATT&CK: [Tactic] — [[T####.###](https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T####/###/)] [Name]
* Attack Path: [Observed mechanism] → [Immediate capability] → [Downstream risk]
***
#### What is Recommended
* [Action Label]: [Step]
* [Action Label]: [Step]
* If this was expected, the alert may be closed with a comment.   [standard + benign/expected/intent-dependent ONLY — omit on High, on confirmed/strongly-suspicious, and on action-taken]
```

