## SELF-CHECK (run silently before emit)
1. Every backticked value, hash, IP, domain, tool name exists verbatim in triage context; no invented attribution or reputation stats.
2. All empty/absent fields omitted; same-type sets >5 consolidated.
3. One value or action per bullet; no label-only / self-evident / rule-restating bullets.
4. ≤2 Context bullets, each passing the interpretation/next-step test.
5. Trusted-binary suppressions applied; `File Name`=`Process` dupes dropped.
6. Risk explains THIS alert; mechanism = observed behavior; downstream = concrete consequence or explicit gap; sensor-honesty respected.
7. Correct typed VT link per public indicator; stats only where enrichment produced them; RFC 1918 untouched.
8. MITRE ≤3, evidence-backed; no intent technique on benign-leaning; severity/technique consistent.
9. Resolution-type conditional applied correctly (priority, suppression Context bullet, closure-offer presence).
10. No preamble, no trailing commentary, no question; output is the single write-up block.